 abstract     = {This is a case study of how one child learned to write in a computer-rich setting. Although computer access did affect her learning significantly, the details presented here go beyond supporting that claim. They provide a simple example of what a computer-based introduction to writing might be like for other children. We conclude with a short discussion of issues raised by the study.},
